#30504
The Foundation~
You're standing in the south western corner of a cavernous room.  The same
red, gold-trimmed carpet covers the floor of this expansive space.  You can
see nine strange grey pillars running from floor to ceiling.  They appear to
be at least twice as wide as the largest oaks you've seen in the forest.  The
walls and ceiling are the same cloudy, opaque crystal, polished to a smooth
and glossy finish.  The room continues onward to the north and east.  There is
a hallway leading to the south of here.  
~
